coming to get you, hmm?

323
00:18:03,996 --> 00:18:07,397
Wow, check that out.
Ooh, look at that.

324
00:18:07,433 --> 00:18:09,901
-Faberge.
-Oh, baby.

325
00:18:09,935 --> 00:18:12,802
Gold enamel, diamond inlay.

326
00:18:12,838 --> 00:18:14,328
Oh, yeah, I have it now.

327
00:18:14,373 --> 00:18:16,534
Yeah, baby.
And I got the score, baby.

328
00:18:16,575 --> 00:18:18,167
Is that not the score
or what, huh?

329
00:18:18,210 --> 00:18:21,839
Fun, too.
Like an Easter egg hunt.

330
00:18:23,249 --> 00:18:24,910
You want to hop upstairs,
and I'll just work this floor?

331
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:27,714
You called it. You called it.

332
00:18:27,753 --> 00:18:29,516
Thanks.

333
00:18:29,555 --> 00:18:32,217
All right. You wanna do it?
