379
00:20:49,061 --> 00:20:50,722
-What?
-That's my ring.

380
00:20:50,796 --> 00:20:53,060
Stop trippin', all right?
This is my ring.

381
00:20:53,098 --> 00:20:55,760
Ha! Son of a bitch! He was gonna
waltz out of here...

382
00:20:55,801 --> 00:20:57,132
