385
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:03,008
Look, my girlfriend
gave me the ring.

386
00:21:03,042 --> 00:21:04,532
If I don't come home
with my ring--

387
00:21:04,577 --> 00:21:07,205
Give me the ring. Give me it.

388
00:21:07,246 --> 00:21:08,645
This is my ring.

389
00:21:10,282 --> 00:21:12,375
