with the perp in custody.

415
00:22:24,356 --> 00:22:27,621
What? Hey! Hey, you! Stop!

416
00:22:29,695 --> 00:22:31,595
Shit! What's going on?

417
00:22:31,630 --> 00:22:33,188
That son of a bitch!

418
00:22:57,956 --> 00:22:59,548
Anything?

419
00:22:59,625 --> 00:23:01,058
Nothing. Clear. Let's go.

420
00:23:23,582 --> 00:23:25,982
I want my damn ring!

421
00:23:29,421 --> 00:23:31,184
You don't know what you started.

422
00:23:55,948 --> 00:23:58,473
I'll take door number three.

423
00:24:02,755 --> 00:24:04,188
Gotta go!

424
00:24:19,304 --> 00:24:22,273
Hello, honey bun.
How was your day?

425
00:24:22,307 --> 00:24:24,241
Good.

426
00:24:30,282 --> 00:24:32,273
What's the matter?

427
00:24:36,588 --> 00:24:37,748
Well, was it bad?

428
00:24:42,895 --> 00:24:44,055
Go on.

429
00:24:47,065 --> 00:24:48,692
I lost the ring.

430
00:24:50,669 --> 00:24:55,629
Oh, Kevin,
I just gave you the ring.

431
00:24:55,674 --> 00:24:59,337
