433
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:05,248
Of all the lousy, jerkological,
cheap-shot stickups...

434
00:25:05,284 --> 00:25:06,410
this has gotta take the cake.

435
00:25:06,451 --> 00:25:09,477
-You got that right.
-Robbed by a householder...

436
00:25:09,521 --> 00:25:11,580
