440
00:25:20,332 --> 00:25:21,594
Sixteen thousand.

441
00:25:21,633 --> 00:25:23,396
What's in that cigar
you're smoking, huh?

442
00:25:23,435 --> 00:25:26,165
Come on, the Fabergé egg alone--

443
00:25:26,238 --> 00:25:27,500
Nice. Don't want it.
It's hard to move.

444
00:25:27,573 --> 00:25:30,440
-Can't move it.
-The damn car, OK?

445
00:25:30,475 --> 00:25:31,567
It's worth--

446
00:25:31,643 --> 00:25:34,669
OK, I'll give you six and a half
for the car.

447
00:25:34,746 --> 00:25:36,839
Round it off to twenty-one five.

448
00:25:36,882 --> 00:25:38,782
That's because
I raised you as my own...

449
00:25:38,817 --> 00:25:41,877
and I'm happy to see you
back in the business.

450
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,649
-Sixteen.
-Sixteen.

451
00:25:43,689 --> 00:25:47,352
-Plus six and a half.
-Half, right.

452
00:25:47,392 --> 00:25:50,452
-Is twenty-one five?
-Man, look. Six...

453
00:25:51,730 --> 00:25:53,755
Twenty-one, fifteen, twenty...

454
00:25:54,867 --> 00:25:56,357
Don't worry about it.

455
00:25:58,036 --> 00:25:59,628
Look here, it's late, all right?

456
00:25:59,705 --> 00:26:01,605
I wanted to see
if you're on your game...

457
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:04,074
so I took a shot at you.
That's all I did.

458
00:26:04,109 --> 00:26:05,906
Man...

459
00:26:05,944 --> 00:26:08,435
I just feel like I'm getting
robbed by everybody tonight.

460
00:26:11,917 --> 00:26:14,078
Come on, Kevin,
it's not that bad.

461
00:26:14,119 --> 00:26:16,644
Why are you so upset?

462
00:26:16,688 --> 00:26:18,485
Why am I so upset?

463
00:26:19,691 --> 00:26:21,818
Baby, let me show you something.

464
00:26:21,860 --> 00:26:23,987
You see this?

465
00:26:24,029 --> 00:26:28,193
