and obsessed by these.

467
00:26:32,204 --> 00:26:35,196
Why?
It's what it represents.

468
00:26:35,274 --> 00:26:37,708
Power, taste, superiority.

469
00:26:37,743 --> 00:26:39,005
That's all in the mind...

470
00:26:39,044 --> 00:26:41,638
of the person
who puts a price on it.

471
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:44,080
What's it mean to me?

472
00:26:44,116 --> 00:26:45,708
Not a damn thing.

473
00:26:45,751 --> 00:26:48,219
Too hard to fence.

474
00:26:48,253 --> 00:26:51,222
Now, the ring,
on the other hand...

475
00:26:51,256 --> 00:26:52,848
is priceless.

476
00:26:52,891 --> 00:26:56,725
