the day my life changed--

477
00:26:56,762 --> 00:26:58,423
the day I met you.

478
00:26:58,463 --> 00:27:00,158
Wow.

479
00:27:08,607 --> 00:27:10,040
Let's go, Monty.
Let's see what you got.

480
00:27:13,946 --> 00:27:16,141
Ooh, bull's-eye!

481
00:27:16,181 --> 00:27:17,808
Game, set, match.

482
00:27:22,955 --> 00:27:24,422
