492
00:27:48,814 --> 00:27:51,681
-Son of a bitch.
-Sir!

493
00:27:51,717 --> 00:27:53,241
Shut up.

494
00:27:54,619 --> 00:27:58,282
Does Lutetia
know about the, uh...

495
00:27:58,323 --> 00:28:00,416
About the young lady?
So far not.

496
00:28:00,459 --> 00:28:02,689
